            "questionId": 5374,
            "questionText": "<p>A company is adopting serverless computing for some of its new services. A development team needs to create a serverless infrastructure by using AWS Serverless Application Model (AWS SAM). All infrastructure must be deployed by using AWS CloudFormation templates.<br><br>What should the development team do to meet these requirements?</p>",
            "explanation": "<p>üìù <u>T√≥m t·∫Øt ƒë·ªÅ:</u></p><ul><li><p>Company adopting serverless computing</p></li><li><p>Development team c·∫ßn t·∫°o <strong>serverless infrastructure b·∫±ng AWS SAM</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>All infrastructure ph·∫£i deployed b·∫±ng CloudFormation templates</strong></p></li><li><p>H·ªèi: development team ph·∫£i l√†m g√¨?</p></li></ul><p></p><p>‚úÖ <u>ƒê√°p √°n ƒë√∫ng:</u></p><p><strong>Add a Transform section to the CloudFormation templates. Use the AWS SAM syntax to define the resources.</strong></p><ul><li><p>AWS SAM l√† extension c·ªßa CloudFormation, require <strong>Transform section</strong> v·ªõi value <code>AWS::Serverless-2016-10-31</code></p></li><li><p>Transform section cho ph√©p s·ª≠ d·ª•ng SAM syntax (AWS::Serverless::Function, AWS::Serverless::API) trong CloudFormation template</p></li><li><p>CloudFormation t·ª± ƒë·ªông transform SAM syntax th√†nh standard CloudFormation resources khi deploy</p></li><li><p>ƒê√¢y l√† c√°ch ch√≠nh th·ª©c ƒë·ªÉ integrate SAM v·ªõi CloudFormation</p></li></ul><p></p><p><u>C√°c ƒë√°p √°n sai:</u></p><p>‚ùå <strong>Add a Resources section to the CloudFormation templates that contains AWS::Lambda::Function resources.</strong></p><ul><li><p>AWS::Lambda::Function l√† standard CloudFormation resource, kh√¥ng ph·∫£i SAM</p></li><li><p>ƒê·ªÅ b√†i y√™u c·∫ßu d√πng AWS SAM, kh√¥ng ph·∫£i plain CloudFormation</p></li><li><p>SAM resource types b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu v·ªõi AWS::Serverless::, kh√¥ng ph·∫£i AWS::Lambda::</p></li></ul><p></p><p>‚ùå <strong>Add a Mappings section to the CloudFormation templates that contains AWS::Serverless::Function and AWS::Serverless::API.</strong></p><ul><li><p>Mappings section d√πng ƒë·ªÉ define key-value pairs, kh√¥ng ph·∫£i define resources</p></li><li><p>SAM resources ph·∫£i define trong Resources section, kh√¥ng ph·∫£i Mappings</p></li><li><p>Sai syntax v√† structure</p></li></ul><p></p><p>‚ùå <strong>Add a Parameters section to the CloudFormation templates that specifies the relevant AWS SAM Globals section.</strong></p><ul><li><p>Parameters section d√πng ƒë·ªÉ pass values v√†o template</p></li><li><p>Globals section l√† SAM-specific config, kh√¥ng li√™n quan ƒë·∫øn Parameters</p></li><li><p>Kh√¥ng ƒë·ªß ƒë·ªÉ enable SAM syntax - v·∫´n c·∫ßn Transform section</p></li></ul><p></p><p>üîë <u>Tips and tricks:</u></p><ul><li><p>\"AWS SAM\" + \"CloudFormation template\" ‚Üí <strong>Transform section</strong> v·ªõi <code>AWS::Serverless-2016-10-31</code></p></li><li><p>SAM template structure: Transform + Resources (v·ªõi AWS::Serverless:: types)</p></li><li><p>Transform section convert SAM syntax ‚Üí standard CloudFormation</p></li><li><p>SAM resource types: AWS::Serverless::Function, AWS::Serverless::API, AWS::Serverless::SimpleTable</p></li><li><p>Kh√¥ng c√≥ Transform = kh√¥ng th·ªÉ d√πng SAM syntax</p></li></ul><p></p><p>üìñ <u>Reference:</u></p><ul><li><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/serverless-application-model/latest/developerguide/sam-specification-template-anatomy.html\">AWS SAM template anatomy</a></p></li></ul>",
            "correctAnswer": [
                "<p>Add a Transform section to the CloudFormation templates. Use the AWS SAM syntax to define the resources.</p>"
            ],
            "selectedAnswers": null,
